playSMS gateway module for clickatell.com
Incoming SMS use gnokii model (spool directory, but dont have tobe gnokii) or callback URL
Outgoing SMS use clickatell.com

Register your self at Clickatell website
and take a note of your username, password, client ID and API ID
those items required for gateway module configuration

Dont forget to point callback setting on Clickatell control panel
to callback.php in this directory
eg:
prior to 0.9.5.1:
http://your_playsms_website/plugin/gateway/clickatell/callback.php
since 0.9.5.1:
http://your_playsms_website/index.php?app=call&cat=gateway&plugin=clickatell&access=callback

Plugin	: Gateway Clickatell for playSMS
Author	: Anton Raharja
Release	: 100925
License	: GPL
